Marion Laboratories Inc saidits board declared a two-for-one common stock split in the formof a dividend, with distribution April 21, record March 25.    The board also said it intends to increase the regularquarterly dividend by 43 pct, to five cts a share, reflectingthe split. It said the increase will be declared at the May1987 board meeting and reflected in regular payments beginningin July 1987. Reuter&#3;